					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">On an NES with an official controller (NES-004 or NES-039), Right will always be pressed in a glitch read. This can be used as an optimization if you detect an official controller at power-on.<br /><br />NOTE: Controllers other than NES-004 or NES-039, particularly the Four Score accessory (NES-034) and some unlicensed controllers, do not obey this rule. Test for this when powering on the system by seeing if reads 9 through 16 are all 1.</div>

